from thinkdsp import SinSignal, CosSignal

sin_C4 = SinSignal(freq=261.63, amp=0.1)
cos_E4 = CosSignal(freq=329.93, amp=0.1)
sin_G4 = SinSignal(freq=392, amp=0.1)
cos_C5 = CosSignal(freq=523.25, amp=0.1)

my_signal = sin_C4 + cos_E4 + sin_G4 + cos_C5
my_signal_wave = my_signal.make_wave(duration=1)
my_signal.plot()
my_signal_wave.make_audio()

def stretch(wave, factor):
  wave.ts *= factor
  wave.framerate /= factor
